commit.message:
Stop installing README.rst to sys.prefix

Remove the `data_files` entry in `setup.py` that caused the `README.rst`
file being installed into `sys.prefix` (i.e. as `/usr/README.rst`).
This definitely isn't a correct location for documentation.
